@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About KhumaloCraft Emporium";
}

<style>
    /* Style for dark background */
    body {
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
    }

    /* Style for about container */
    .about-container {
        background-color: #222;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Style for about title */
    .about-title {
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Style for about content */
    .about-content {
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
</style>

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="about-container">
    <h2 class="about-title">Welcome to KhumaloCraft Emporium</h2>
    <p class="about-content">At KhumaloCraft Emporium, where creativity meets commerce! Founded by James Khumalo, a visionary entrepreneur, our mission is to revolutionize the way handcrafted products are showcased and sold worldwide.</p>
    <p class="about-content">James Khumalo embarked on this journey with a clear vision in mind: to connect artisans from every corner of the globe with a discerning audience passionate about unique and high-quality craftsmanship. However, he realized that achieving this dream would require more than just passion; it would demand innovation, scalability, and a user-friendly platform.</p>
    <p class="about-content">At KhumaloCraft Emporium, we understand the importance of leveraging technology to enable global accessibility, scalability, and a seamless user experience. Our team is dedicated to harnessing the power of cloud computing and advanced Azure features to create a platform that not only showcases artisans' craftwork but also provides a secure and enjoyable shopping experience for customers worldwide.</p>
    <p class="about-content">We face numerous challenges, from making critical decisions on cloud service models and deployment strategies to designing an efficient database schema that ensures scalability with our platform's growth. However, we are committed to overcoming these challenges and delivering a platform that exceeds expectations.</p>
    <p class="about-content">With advanced features such as search capabilities, notifications, serverless services, and automation, KhumaloCraft Emporium aims to set a new standard for online artisanal marketplaces. Our goal is to create a web application that not only stores artisans' craftwork but also enables customers globally to access and order their favorite pieces with ease.</p>
    <p class="about-content">Thank you for joining us on this exciting journey. Together, let's celebrate creativity, craftsmanship, and connection at KhumaloCraft Emporium.</p>
</div>
